{"tid":1953653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"4月1日應當訂為公眾假期","createTime":"2020-04-01T09:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T10:03:13.000Z","uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca83d636cfb14d8536b44cd8c8e54f765ca40e3d","tid":1953653,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10219333257456739&amp;set=a.1933727497437&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10219333257456739%26set%3Da.1933727497437%26type%3D3&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=7be212b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10219333257456739&amp;set=a.1933727497437&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n【4月1日應當訂為公眾假期】<br />\n<br />\n是的，我也是一個「後哥迷」&mdash;第一次認識哥哥就是17年前的今天。多虧了互聯網的發達，容許我和其他「後哥迷」有機會欣賞哥哥的美好。<br />\n<br />\n17年後，我們對哥哥的思念越發熱烈。哥哥既有英國貴族的氣質，亦有東方文人俠士的儒雅。為人更是高風亮節，一見令人心醉。<br />\n<br />\n哥哥在台上最令我深刻的印象，就係佢好害怕會被大家遺忘。當哥哥唱出《明星》中「當你見到天上星星，可有想起我」一句時，令人潸然淚下。哥哥，你又教人如何可以忘記你？<br />\n<br />\n或許我們懷念哥哥的同時，亦在懷念香港往日生活的美好。我們慨嘆樂壇影圈未有人接班哥哥，更憤恨政壇充斥鼠輩宵小為禍人間。<br />\n<br />\n我們每年都慶祝端午節紀念屈原，或許我們更應該珍惜哥哥，這是我們香港人的集體回憶。就如同我們不會忘記一眾逝去、在囚、流亡的手足，這份只屬於香港人的美好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6rmzUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6rmzUA.jpg&h=6bc916cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🥥Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/coconutinnocent/shop/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcoconutinnocent%2Fshop%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=f136c3ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/coconutinnocent/shop/</a><br />\n🥥Instagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/coconutinnocent/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcoconutinnocent%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=5361856e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/coconutinnocent/</a><br />\n🥥Telegram Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/coconutinnocent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcoconutinnocent&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=60a638aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/coconutinnocent</a><br />\n🥥carousell<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.carousell.com/coconutinnocent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.carousell.com%2Fcoconutinnocent&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=9a975bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.carousell.com/coconutinnocent</a>"},{"pid":"7792960bd5f76393be40b5ad6ff7fc3e97a55bd1","tid":1953653,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d297198115632f141252d24c2fe2e703c9f39a","tid":1953653,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24982372a307da90a3651ff78e1b789c9c3e0be","tid":1953653,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n如果揀一個明星代表香港,一定係揀哥哥<br />\n雖然佢係50後,但而家睇返佢後生時完全唔覺個LOOK過氣<br />\n亞洲影響力又大,紅到韓國<br />\n成龍雖然更出名,但黑料咁多,又唔靚仔"},{"pid":"624690ec82dc069905767762231c9fc94e04a5f7","tid":1953653,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24982372a307da90a3651ff78e1b789c9c3e0be","tid":1953653,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n如果揀一個明星代表香港,一定係揀哥哥<br />\n雖然佢係50後,但而家睇返佢後生時完全唔覺個LOOK過氣<br />\n亞洲影響力又大,紅到韓國<br />\n成龍雖然更出名,但黑料咁多,又唔靚仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wWPWYqSkDaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwWPWYqSkDaY&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLG